{"tid":142672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得買旗個d人其實係想做咗善事想話俾人知","createTime":"2017-03-04T03:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T07:21:07.000Z","uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cccf2a688f335e7cc3ba5b99fc6b654300da8cab","tid":142672,"uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"我都買咗，因為d小朋友好煩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25dc957830033c757dedd280ed36c6788b3d6390","tid":142672,"uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bbc05c2bd5870e4f85614d79966eca44abbaf5","tid":142672,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yzp22Wt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzp22Wt.jpg&h=5a2b085e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf936a1c1c5ff5694ec4fedd1cd0c54586722f3c","tid":142672,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"只係想話比人知<br />\n已經施捨左<br />\n唔該唔好再煩我"},{"pid":"8c7d761615dc360c6b987fa79e99407c85c2a3b4","tid":142672,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"最撚憎咩野幫我買枝旗<br />\n又唔撚知你咩機構 九唔撚搭八"},{"pid":"29edd2f081eaad14b57925aef9363d262d3324ea","tid":142672,"uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"有d小朋友積極琴好似有佣收咁。"},{"pid":"e4def54dcda3af9a78a0d8177e1fffefad825061","tid":142672,"uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d小朋友積極到好似有佣收咁。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6ee4c82c1aaef956b9f699cdfea8e268264f933e","tid":142672,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有d小朋友積極到好似有佣收咁。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n小朋友唔可以用利益去諗佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該單純只係覺得自己賣得多旗威威豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b9bbcd124f3e75afdea3de2e426f5ede5ae814","tid":142672,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"根本就係利用啲小朋友<br />\n啲人見到小朋友就發晒姣<br />\n尤其女人<br />\n「小朋友好可愛呀 ，姐姐幫你買枝旗呀」<br />\n<br />\n反而啲家長帶個小朋友去賣旗真係唔知咩心態<br />\n以為呢啲活動可以幫小朋友將來升到好中學？<br />\n定以為賣旗真係可以幫到好多人？"},{"pid":"11e96b390ae772a9d119e6814401ad3309918396","tid":142672,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚憎咩野幫我買枝旗<br />\n又唔撚知你咩機構 九唔撚搭八</blockquote><br />\n咪就係<br />\n幫你買定幫受惠者買呀<br />\n你一黎到講下咩機構/用黎做咩仲好<br />\n「你好呀我係連登㗎<br />\n我地希望籌款去幫助新會然<br />\n去融入連登㗎<br />\n請你買枝旗支持下呀」<br />\n咁樣就可能買"},{"pid":"52bdcc77175732ce10e3722f1de7814a2de57150","tid":142672,"uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有d小朋友積極到好似有佣收咁。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n小朋友唔可以用利益去諗佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該單純只係覺得自己賣得多旗威威豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得賣旗意義不大，又有金錢利益，<br />\n我明白家長想小朋友做義工，我覺得去老人院，沙灘清理垃圾仲有意思。"},{"pid":"5b2413efb230d9cf81472872795328967c44cd08","tid":142672,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:56:38.000Z","msg":"依家九成所謂慈善組織根本搵笨七做形象功程,好多機構本身有錢到仆街唔係就抽九成手續費,慈善兩個字變晒質"},{"pid":"ca8fb6df59c0a9f00765859e57623ae0aa7e987f","tid":142672,"u